    <entry>
      <title>第一周_初见JavaScript垃圾回收</title>
      <link href="/2020/07/06/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8-%E5%88%9D%E8%A7%81JavaScript%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E5%9B%9E%E6%94%B6/"/>
      <url>/2020/07/06/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8-%E5%88%9D%E8%A7%81JavaScript%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E5%9B%9E%E6%94%B6/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="引入"><a href="#引入" class="headerlink" title="引入"></a>引入</h1><ul><li>JavaScript 中的内存管理是自动执行的，而且是不可见的</li><li>我们创建基本类型、对象、函数……所有这些都需要内存</li></ul><p>当不再需要某样东西（内存）时会发生什么? JavaScript 引擎是如何发现并清理它?</p><h1 id="垃圾回收原则"><a href="#垃圾回收原则" class="headerlink" title="垃圾回收原则"></a>垃圾回收原则</h1><h2 id="可达性"><a href="#可达性" class="headerlink" title="可达性"></a>可达性</h2><ul><li>JavaScript 中内存管理的主要概念是可达性——<strong>那些以某种方式可访问或可用的值，它们被保证存储在内存中</strong></li><li><strong>JavaScript 引擎中有一个后台进程称为垃圾回收器，它监视所有对象，并删除那些不可访问的对象</strong></li></ul><h3 id="根"><a href="#根" class="headerlink" title="根"></a>根</h3><p>一组基本的固有可达值，由于显而易见的原因无法删除，如：</p><ul><li>本地函数的局部变量和参数</li><li>当前嵌套调用链上的其他函数和参数</li><li>全局变量</li><li>还有一些其他的、内部的</li></ul><p><strong>这些值称为根</strong></p><h3 id="可访问"><a href="#可访问" class="headerlink" title="可访问"></a>可访问</h3><p><strong>如果引用或引用链可以从根访问任何其他值，则认为该值是可访问的</strong></p><h2 id="简单例子"><a href="#简单例子" class="headerlink" title="简单例子"></a>简单例子</h2><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript"><span class="token keyword">let</span> user <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>    name<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">'john'</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></code></pre><p><img src="1.png" alt="简单引用数据"></p><ul><li>这里存在一个对象引用</li><li>如果 user 的值被覆盖，则引用丢失</li></ul><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript">user <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">null</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></code></pre><p><img src="2.png" alt="不可达数据"></p><p><strong>现在 John 变成不可达的状态，没有办法访问它，没有对它的引用。垃圾回收器将丢弃 John 数据并释放内存</strong></p><h2 id="相互关联"><a href="#相互关联" class="headerlink" title="相互关联"></a>相互关联</h2><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript"><span class="token keyword">function</span> marry <span class="token punctuation">(</span>man<span class="token punctuation">,</span> woman<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>  woman<span class="token punctuation">.</span>husban <span class="token operator">=</span> man<span class="token punctuation">;</span>  man<span class="token punctuation">.</span>wife <span class="token operator">=</span> woman<span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>    father<span class="token punctuation">:</span> man<span class="token punctuation">,</span>    mother<span class="token punctuation">:</span> woman  <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token keyword">let</span> family <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token function">marry</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>  name<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token string">"John"</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>  name<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token string">"Ann"</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></code></pre><p>内存结构：</p><p><img src="3.png" alt="内存结构"></p><p>现在删除两个引用</p><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript"><span class="token keyword">delete</span> family<span class="token punctuation">.</span>father<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token keyword">delete</span> family<span class="token punctuation">.</span>mother<span class="token punctuation">.</span>husband<span class="token punctuation">;</span></code></pre><p><img src="4.png" alt="内存结构"></p><p><strong>输出引用无关紧要</strong>。只有传入的对象才能使对象可访问，因此，John 现在是不可访问的，并将从内存中删除所有不可访问的数据</p><p>垃圾回收之后：</p><p><img src="5.png" alt="内存结构"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> JavaScript </tag>
            
            <tag> 前端 </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Vue基础</title>
      <link href="/2020/06/25/Vue%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/"/>
      <url>/2020/06/25/Vue%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="准备开始"><a href="#准备开始" class="headerlink" title="准备开始"></a>准备开始</h1><h2 id="历史"><a href="#历史" class="headerlink" title="历史"></a>历史</h2><p>angular 2009年</p><p>react 2013年</p><p>vue 2014年，(尤雨溪)中国人创建，现在美籍</p><h2 id="框架和库"><a href="#框架和库" class="headerlink" title="框架和库"></a>框架和库</h2><p>库(小而精)</p><ul><li>jQuery库 -&gt; DOM操作+请求</li><li>art-template -&gt; 模板引擎</li></ul><p>框架(大而全，可能包含多个库)</p><ul><li>DOM操作+请求+模板引擎+路由功能</li></ul><p>代码上</p><ul><li>库是引用 js 文件，调用函数，自己把控库的代码</li><li>框架在帮我们运行我们写好的代码<ul><li>初始化自身的行为</li><li>执行你编写的代码</li><li>释放一些资源<h2 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h2></li></ul></li></ul><p>直接官网下载 js 文件</p><p><strong>推荐</strong>：使用 npm 进行下载(有效配合其他模块使用)</p><h1 id="模板语法"><a href="#模板语法" class="headerlink" title="模板语法"></a>模板语法</h1><h2 id="基础"><a href="#基础" class="headerlink" title="基础"></a>基础</h2><pre class=" language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class="token attr-name">id</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>app<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>        {{msg}}    //模板标记    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//script</span><span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">Vue</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    el<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">'#app'</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//绑定目标</span>    data<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//数据属性(正确用法在指令中)</span>        msg<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">'haha'</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    template<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token template-string"><span class="token string">`&lt;div>{{msg}}&lt;/div>`</span></span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//直接定义渲染目标，这将会跳过原html中书写的，不去渲染</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></code></pre><p>模板标记支持变量运算，DOM操作,比如</p><pre class=" language-html"><code class="language-html">{{1+1}}    //渲染为2{{str.split('').reserve().join('')}}    //会将数据属性中的str变量翻转{{1>2?'真':'假'}}    //渲染为假</code></pre><p><strong>注意只能包含单个表达式</strong></p><h2 id="Vue对象"><a href="#Vue对象" class="headerlink" title="Vue对象"></a>Vue对象</h2><p>new的基础上可以返回一个Vue对象</p><p>内部拥有我们定义的数据</p><p>内部早就定义好的属性会以$开头</p><h1 id="指令"><a href="#指令" class="headerlink" title="指令"></a>指令</h1><h2 id="简介"><a href="#简介" class="headerlink" title="简介"></a>简介</h2><ul><li>vue提供了一些对于页面+数据更为方便的输出，这些操作叫做指令，以 v-xxx表示</li><li>指令封装了一些DOM行为</li><li>注意，指令进行操作时内部的值均为data数据，如果使用原生形态，内部则是字符串</li></ul><h2 id="v-text-v-html"><a href="#v-text-v-html" class="headerlink" title="v-text v-html"></a>v-text v-html</h2><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript">data<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token keyword">function</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//其实这里应该要用函数返回值，后期讲解为什么，以后就用函数形式</span>    <span class="token keyword">return</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        msg<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">'指令操作'</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>template<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token template-string"><span class="token string">`    &lt;h2>{{msg}}&lt;/h2>    &lt;p v-text='msg'>&lt;/p> //相当于innertext    &lt;div v-html='msg'>&lt;/div> //相当于innerhtml`</span></span></code></pre><p>注意 Mustache 语法(双大括号)，会把其中的内容解释为普通文本，如果是 html 代码，请使用 v-html之类的</p><h2 id="v-if-v-else-v-show"><a href="#v-if-v-else-v-show" class="headerlink" title="v-if v-else v-show"></a>v-if v-else v-show</h2><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript">data<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token keyword">function</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">return</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        msg<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token boolean">true</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>template<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token template-string"><span class="token string">`    &lt;p v-if='msg'>if显示&lt;/p>    //字符串内的值为真，则显示    &lt;p v-else>else显示&lt;/p>    //为假显示else    &lt;p v-if='Math.random()>0.5'>随机显示&lt;/p> //值必须是字符串，可以嵌套函数    &lt;p v-show='msg'>show显示&lt;/p>    //show显示，和if差不多`</span></span></code></pre><h3 id="if和show的区别"><a href="#if和show的区别" class="headerlink" title="if和show的区别"></a>if和show的区别</h3><p>v-if 实际上是对DOM中的 appendChild() 和 removeChild() 的操作，v-show 是对 css 的 display 属性的操作，<strong>所以 v-if 开销较大，不适合频繁切换的组件</strong></p><h3 id="v-if-else"><a href="#v-if-else" class="headerlink" title="v-if-else"></a>v-if-else</h3><p>字面意思，可以多重嵌套 if</p><h3 id="key管理可复用元素"><a href="#key管理可复用元素" class="headerlink" title="key管理可复用元素"></a>key管理可复用元素</h3><p>Vue 会尽可能高效地渲染元素，通常会复用已有元素而不是从头开始渲染</p><p>也就是说，相同的元素标签，Vue不会重新渲染，只是替换变化的值</p><p>使用 key 属性标志需要区别的元素，即可重新渲染</p><h2 id="v-bind"><a href="#v-bind" class="headerlink" title="v-bind"></a>v-bind</h2><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript">data<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token keyword">function</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">return</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        msg<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">'hahaah'</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>template<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token template-string"><span class="token string">`    &lt;div v-bind:class='msg'>&lt;/div> //渲染后div会得到一个 hahaah 的class    &lt;div :class='msg'>&lt;/div> //v-bind的简写形式`</span></span></code></pre><h2 id="v-on"><a href="#v-on" class="headerlink" title="v-on"></a>v-on</h2><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript">template<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token template-string"><span class="token string">`    &lt;div v-on:事件名='调用函数'>&lt;/div> //绑定事件函数    &lt;div @:事件名='调用函数'>&lt;/div> //v-on的简写`</span></span>methods<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token function">待调用函数名</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre><p>注意：当调用函数重新渲染时，是整个模板重新渲染</p><h2 id="v-for"><a href="#v-for" class="headerlink" title="v-for"></a>v-for</h2><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript">data<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    lists<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span>        <span class="token punctuation">{</span>id<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>name<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">'hah'</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        <span class="token punctuation">{</span>id<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>name<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">'ladjf'</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    obj<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        name<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">'tyt'</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        age<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">'19'</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>template<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token template-string"><span class="token string">`    &lt;ul>        &lt;li v-for='item in lists'> //遍历数组            &lt;h5 v-html='item.id'>&lt;/h5>            &lt;h5 v-html='item.name'>&lt;/h5>        &lt;/li>    &lt;/ul>    //一个ul列表，并且遍历data中的lists，然后输出数据到视图上    &lt;ul>    //遍历对象        &lt;li v-for='(value.key) in person'> //注意value遍历person，key则是索引            {{key}}={{value}}        &lt;/li>    &lt;/ul>`</span></span></code></pre><h2 id="v-model-双向数据绑定"><a href="#v-model-双向数据绑定" class="headerlink" title="v-model 双向数据绑定"></a>v-model 双向数据绑定</h2><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript">templat<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token template-string"><span class="token string">`    &lt;input type="text" v-model="msg">    &lt;h3 v-html="msg">&lt;/h3>`</span></span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token function">data</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">return</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        msg<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">'hahaha'</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//当input的值变化时，h3的值也会变化</span></code></pre><p>v-model 实际上是一种语法糖，可以用以下组合实现</p><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript">v<span class="token operator">-</span>value<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"xxx"</span> v<span class="token operator">-</span>on<span class="token punctuation">:</span>input<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token keyword">function</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>e<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>msg<span class="token operator">=</span>e<span class="token punctuation">.</span>target<span class="token punctuation">.</span>value<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//注意this指向实例化的Vue对象，e.target指向触发事件的元素</span></code></pre><h1 id="组件"><a href="#组件" class="headerlink" title="组件"></a>组件</h1><h2 id="局部组件"><a href="#局部组件" class="headerlink" title="局部组件"></a>局部组件</h2><p>仅保留el，其余的属性保存在一个<strong>对象</strong>中</p><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//1.声明局部组件</span><span class="token keyword">let</span> son<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token function">data</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token operator">...</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    template<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token template-string"><span class="token string">``</span></span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    methods<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token operator">...</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token operator">...</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token keyword">let</span> all<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">Vue</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    el<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">'#app'</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    components<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//2.挂载局部组件</span>        son    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    template<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token template-string"><span class="token string">`         &lt;son>&lt;/son>`</span></span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//3.使用局部组件</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></code></pre><h2 id="全局组件"><a href="#全局组件" class="headerlink" title="全局组件"></a>全局组件</h2><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript">Vue<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">component</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'组件名字'</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    template<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token template-string"><span class="token string">`        ...    `</span></span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token function">data</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token keyword">return</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token operator">...</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//全局组件的声明方式</span></code></pre><p>然后可以在任何组件中是使用、</p><h2 id="数据传递-基础"><a href="#数据传递-基础" class="headerlink" title="数据传递(基础)"></a>数据传递(基础)</h2><h3 id="父组件-→-子组件"><a href="#父组件-→-子组件" class="headerlink" title="父组件 → 子组件"></a>父组件 → 子组件</h3><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//1.在使用子组件时绑定属性</span><span class="token function">data</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token keyword">return</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>msg<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">'xxx'</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>template<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token template-string"><span class="token string">`    &lt;Vson :childData='msg'/>`</span></span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//2.在子组件内部props绑定属性</span>props<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token string">'childData'</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//3.在子组件中使用</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span>p v<span class="token operator">-</span>html<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">'childData'</span><span class="token operator">></span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>p<span class="token operator">></span></code></pre><p>注意绑定属性后在子组件内部使用绑定名</p><h3 id="子组件-→-父组件"><a href="#子组件-→-父组件" class="headerlink" title="子组件 → 父组件"></a>子组件 → 父组件</h3><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//1.父组件在子组件绑定自定义事件</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span>div @childHandler<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">'change'</span><span class="token operator">></span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>div<span class="token operator">></span>methods<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token function">change</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//2.子组件中触发子组件自定义事件</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span>div @click<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">'changeFather'</span><span class="token operator">></span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>div<span class="token operator">></span>methods<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token function">changeFather</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">$emit</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'childHandler'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//3.$emit 第一个参数是父组件自定义的事件名，可以再传入参数当做父组件事件调用函数的参数</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//4.自定义事件一定通过 $emit 触发</span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
